en_8976904_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – Notorious underworld figure Angoda Lokka’s main lieutenant has been arrested.
en_8976904_1	Police Special Task Force (STF) said the suspect, Sarath Kumara, was arrested at his residence in Kotikawatta this morning (April 3).
en_8976904_2	Police STF personnel also seized a grenade in the possession of the 41-year-old suspect.
en_8976904_3	He is scheduled to be handed over to the Organised Crimes Division, today (April 3).
